title: Must have mac app's
description:
Desktop manager: a spaces like app for mac osx 10.4

Appdelete: creates a file in trash with all files, setting&#039;s ect. for any app you drag to it  in the dock

Spanner: disables hot corners useful in full screen games

Caffeine: keeps your mac awake

tofu splits long text into columns

Handbrake takes files from mac the ripper and turns them into movie(.avi ect) files

Mac the ripper: extracts movie (DVD) files

Disk inventory x: where did all that Space go now? 

Firefox: web browser

And one i forgot to put into the read me is

Tube tv:downloads youtube videos
